messages.text: ugh SO BORED. please shoot me now.
that bad huh?
i mean - it's a school field trip to the theatre...and the theme is: "say no to violence, kids"
so, immense boredom was to be expected??
yeah exactly lol. the only interesting thing happening is the crazy dude a couple of rows in front of me.
he's so fidgety - total nut job - is annoying the shit out of the stuffy old lady sitting next to him. haha.
hilarious
WAIT
what?
omg
I think I just saw something
that’s the whole point of theater haha
no I mean
the nutter a couple of rows from me...I think I saw him take a gun out of his bag!!
what? no way
I’m serious!
isn’t it dark?
I swear I saw it but now I can’t see it anymore
it's nothing dude. you're just bored.
omg I saw it again!! he DEF has a gun. wtf Jared, I am freaking out.
ok so the man has a gun - big deal, it's legal. it's not like he's gonna use it!
everyone is always freaking out about shootings at schools and churches...
but come on - in this town? at the theatre?? no way.
Blake? yt??
did it finally get interesting or something??
OH SHIT!!!
what??? what's going on??
BLAKE?! dude wtf
omg omg omg - HE DID IT
HE PULLED HIS GUN OUT!! He’s shouting
are you serious???
it’s crazy. show's stopped. I'm crouched on the floor, hiding
he’s pointing the gun at everyone
I can’t watch this
omg I’m calling 911
yeah call please!!
I’m really scared Jared. this dude is batshit crazy
he’s screaming and running around hitting people
ok just called them! they said they’re on their way. hang in there bro, it’ll be ok.
OMG
what now??!
he’s holding this girl
Jesus Christ
he’s got the gun at her head
oh god
she’s crying
there’s people arguing with him
he’s not letting go of her!!
omg Blake get away from him!
I saw her before the show
though she was cute. what the hell is happening right now
oh god he’s dragging her around
Jesus Christ stay hidden!!!
he’s saying he’s gonna teach her a lesson
she didn’t go out with him or something. she's shaking
where’s the police? they should be there by now
maybe they’re waiting because they know he has hostages
Blake? keep talking to me man, don’t stop texting
HE SHOT HER!!!!!!!
WHAT
Jared he shot her he shot her omg omg
oh no. I can't believe it
she’s dead man she’s dead
Jesus
she’s dead oh god
blood everywhere
where are you
up in a back row
are you hidden well?
yeah he hasn’t seen me yet
can’t you run away?
no there’s only one exit and he’s in front of it
he SHOT her Jared. I’m gonna die in here!!!
NO you’re not! the police are coming, hold on!
now he’s walking around
I’m crawling to keep avoiding him. I think I just peed myself a little
whatever just keep crawling away from him!
what if he smells it???
just STAY HIDDEN!
he’s coming my way
STAY HIDDEN!!!!
he grabbed a guy right in front of me
I’m shaking all over
he’s dragging him to the stage
it’s not you! that’s what matters
I can’t take this anymore
he’s gonna kill everyone. one by one. where are the cops??!!
he won’t! just stay patient. I'm sure the cops are figuring everything out.
he’s screaming that he will,
oh god. he’s saying he’s gonna chop the guys hands off
just like in the play!!
jesus he’s mental. why isn’t there a swat team or something in there?
he just pulled out a knife! I can’t watch
ten minutes later
what’s going on? did he do it???
Blake - talk to me, man!! are you ok??
BLAKE!!! I’m freaking out just SAY SOMETHING
this is so fucking TWISTED
YOU’RE ALIVE
yeah and so is everyone else
what??? the girl survived?
she was never shot
? but you said...
they turned on the lights
WTF is going on Blake??
it’s a hoax. the whole thing was a big prank.
WHAT?
it was part of the show
the guy was an actor
gun not real. girl and other guy actors as well. fake blood.
wow no way
I hate them. that was the WORST moment of my life
Jesus that’s sick
I’m gonna SUE them
they’re all smiling now. everyone else is in shock. me too, I think
that is going way, way too far! Jesus. you should point a gun at them see how they feel
NO. no more guns. never again. I’m going home
lol well then I guess it worked. "violence is bad" ;)
ha, yeah - I guess
want me to come over?
yeah, we can play ball or something.
no Call of Duty? lol
NO WAY. see ya soon dude.
